Package: STdiag
Type: Package
Title: This package provides functions to plot a structure-time diagram
Version: 1.0-1
Date: 2012-10-23
Author: Vincent Le Bourlot
Maintainer: Vincent Le Bourlot <vincent.le.bourlot@ens.fr>
Description: This package contains two functions to plot a structure-time 
  diagram with different options concerning the color scale, 
  and the interpolation. An example of the use of the function is given using 
  a sample data set.
Depends: R(>= 2.14.0), lattice, akima, fields
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
License: CeCILL (file LICENSE)
